title: 227: Midseason Awards, Bama's Calvin Ridley
itunes:title: 227: Midseason Awards, Bama's Calvin Ridley
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks hand out midseason awards including MVP and Coach of the Year (4:39). They guys are then joined by Alabama's blue-chip wide receiver Calvin Ridley (34:17). DJ and Bucky also break down their NFL game of the week (15:32) and pick this weekend's college football slate (45:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
